Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita cepat pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanti bertemu lagi.
