Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang bisa melampaui urutan otoritas kita
